{"tid":1081646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★冇錢買樓？神秘男子備蚊帳被鋪上水街頭紮營","createTime":"2019-03-28T11:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T07:03:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c19a8505a1f3cd83cf3206ae6ddd68c9bfd44ca","tid":1081646,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"香港土地供應問題嚴重，有網民於上水發現，有神秘人於路邊「紮營」，因營內備有一個行李箱，故懷疑是遊客所為。雖然身份未能確定，但旁若無人的行為依然令人咋舌！<br />\n<br />\n網民今日凌晨於Facebook專頁「上水人上水事」分享3幅相片，從相中可見一個蚊帳被放置路邊，內裡齊備被鋪、枕頭等床上用品，隨處擺放了不同的如帽子等衣物。除此之外，帳內亦有一個黑色行李箱，在蚊帳內居住的人疑似為遊客，但未能確定「持有人」身份，據稱是一名不明男子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2310000/2310056/SheungShui_thumb_20190328_ch_v2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2310000%2F2310056%2FSheungShui_thumb_20190328_ch_v2_600.jpg&h=40620114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2310056/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2310056%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7ALBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=bcad536e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2310056/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"f4f581d0773f55c1ccd675a870eaabf75c6b9175","tid":1081646,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c128996d8cad6ab7f19f43252cef456bd88ee01","tid":1081646,"uid":178875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"遲下政府會唔會收佢地租差餉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8409eb95cf3715438304713cccf9904c148f497b","tid":1081646,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"大陸人黎"},{"pid":"f124f5045da9373596fcd790d1ec48b1e0492130","tid":1081646,"uid":243693,"like":0,"dis